  "detailed_description": "Lost Recall is puzzle game with skill-based elements. To progress through the level, you'll need to use both your intellect and agility.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use unique abilities of robots</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/f82427e9a05b4de514c9559e3e12016f.poster.avif?t=1697194892\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/f82427e9a05b4de514c9559e3e12016f.webm?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/f82427e9a05b4de514c9559e3e12016f.mp4?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each of the robots has its own unique ability, which will be necessary to solve puzzles. Use the red robot to destroy objects. Move hard-to-reach crates with the blue robot. Or move heavy objects with the purple one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >200 hancrafted levels</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/b7b135ac58c80746cb71fd3bdd6d1f3f.poster.avif?t=1697194892\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/b7b135ac58c80746cb71fd3bdd6d1f3f.webm?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/b7b135ac58c80746cb71fd3bdd6d1f3f.mp4?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each of the levels presents a different challenge. Some will rely on your intellect, while others will demand dexterity. There are also a few that carry a certain mystery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >35 different appearances</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/bca8d0427c63ee4391a8417132d31aaf.poster.avif?t=1697194892\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/bca8d0427c63ee4391a8417132d31aaf.webm?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588760/extras/bca8d0427c63ee4391a8417132d31aaf.mp4?t=1697194892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>While solving puzzles, you'll have the opportunity to unlock new outfits for your robots. Collect them all and choose the ones that fit your style!",
